ks, Alaska|page=7|via = [[Newspapers.com]]}} {{open access}}\n*{{cite news|ref={{harvid|''The Albuquerque Journal''|1975}}|author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.-->|title=Passes Gavel to New President|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/13290573/albuquerque_journal/|accessdate=24 August 2017|newspaper=[[The Albuquerque Journal]]|date=June 22, 1975|location=Albuquerque, New Mexico|page=24|via = [[Newspapers.com]]}} {{open access}}\n*{{cite news|ref={{harvid|''The Fairbanks Daily News-Miner''|1966}}|author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.-->|title=Project Pushed by Volunteers|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/13296726/project_pushed_by_volunteers_fairbanks/|accessdate=23 August 2017|newspaper=[[Fairbanks Daily News-Miner]]|date=January 31, 1966|location=Fairbanks, Alaska|page=3|via = [[Newspapers.com]]}} {{open access}}\n*{{cite news|ref={{harvid|''The Fairbanks Daily News-Miner''|1964}}|author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.-->|title=Resolution Asks State to Recognize Problem|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/13296484/fairbanks_daily_newsminer/|accessdate=23 August 2017|newspaper=[[Fairbanks Daily News-Miner]]|date=October 29, 1964|location=Fairbanks, Alaska|page=9|via = [[Newspapers.com]]}} {{open access}}\n*{{cite news|ref={{harvid|''The San Saba News and Star''|1976}}|author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.-->|title=Resolution Asks State to Recognize Problem|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/13290510/the_san_saba_news_and_star/|accessdate=24 August 2017|publisher=The San Saba News and Star|date=October 21, 1976|location=San Saba, Texas|page=3|via = [[Newspapers.com]]}} {{open access}}\n{{refend}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://vilda.alaska.edu/cdm/ref/collection/cdmg2/id/3786 photograph]\n\n{{Authority control}}\n{{Alaska Women's Hall of Fame}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Fate, Mary Jane}}\n[[Category:1933 births]]\n[[Category:2020 deaths]]\n[[Category:Alaskan Athabaskan people]]\n[[Category:Female Native American leaders]]\n[[Category:American civil rights activis