ood BlueClaws players]]\n[[Category:Major League Baseball pitchers]]\n[[Category:Major League Baseball pitchers who have pitched a perfect game]]\n[[Category:Major League Baseball players with retired numbers]]\n[[Category:National Baseball Hall of Fame inductees]]\n[[Category:National League All-Stars]]\n[[Category:National League wins champions]]\n[[Category:Philadelphia Phillies players]]\n[[Category:People who died at sea]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Denver]]\n[[Category:Tennessee Smokies players]]\n[[Category:Toronto Blue Jays players]]\n[[Category:Syracuse SkyChiefs players]]\n", "name_user": "45.18.138.123", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(\u2192\u200eDeath:Opinion.)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roy_Halladay"}
